## Servers Running
- **Backend**: `http://localhost:8000` (uvicorn --reload)
- **Frontend**: `http://localhost:3000` (Next.js 16 Turbopack)
- **DB**: Neon PostgreSQL via `DATABASE_URL` in [backend/.env](file:///c:/Users/Fagun/Desktop/New%20folder%20%283%29/backend/.env) *(user must fill in)*
- **LLM**: Google Gemini via `GOOGLE_API_KEY` in [backend/.env](file:///c:/Users/Fagun/Desktop/New%20folder%20%283%29/backend/.env) *(user must fill in)*
